---
import AppShell from "../../layouts/AppShell.astro";

const title = "Gastos y suscripciones";
const filterDays = Array.from({ length: 31 }, (_, i) => i + 1);
---

<AppShell title={title}>
  <div data-requires-auth class="hidden"></div>
  <section class="space-y-6 w-full" data-tools-expense-page>
    <header class="space-y-3">
      <a href="/tools" class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 hover:underline">← Herramientas</a>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-start sm:justify-between gap-3">
        <div class="space-y-2 min-w-0 flex-1">
          <h1 class="m-0 text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight">{title}</h1>
          <p class="m-0 text-sm md:text-base text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 max-w-3xl leading-relaxed">
            Tus gastos se quedan en este navegador salvo que tú actives una copia en tu cuenta (botón arriba a la derecha).
            Incluso con copia en la nube, <strong class="font-medium text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">otro usuario de la app no puede abrir tu hoja</strong>: cada uno solo ve lo suyo. Si además usas la frase del cuaderno, la copia sube cifrada y
            <strong class="font-medium text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">ni quien tenga acceso técnico a la base de datos puede leer los importes</strong> sin esa frase (que no guardamos en servidor).
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="relative shrink-0" data-et-sync-host>
          <button
            type="button"
            data-et-sync-popover-toggle
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-xl border border-indigo-200/90 dark:border-indigo-800/80 bg-indigo-50/90 dark:bg-indigo-950/40 px-3 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-indigo-900 dark:text-indigo-100 hover:bg-indigo-100/90 dark:hover:bg-indigo-950/70 shadow-sm"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-haspopup="dialog"
            aria-controls="et-sync-popover-panel"
            id="et-sync-popover-trigger"
          >
            <span class="relative inline-flex h-2 w-2 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-indigo-400 dark:bg-indigo-500 opacity-0" data-et-sync-status-dot aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span>Copia en tu cuenta</span>
            <svg class="h-4 w-4 opacity-70" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"></path>
            </svg>
          </button>
          <div
            id="et-sync-popover-panel"
            data-et-sync-popover
            class="hidden absolute right-0 sm:right-0 left-0 sm:left-auto top-full mt-2 w-[min(100%,22rem)] sm:w-[min(100vw-2rem,24rem)] rounded-2xl border border-gray-200/90 dark:border-gray-800 bg-white/98 dark:bg-gray-950/98 backdrop-blur-md shadow-xl z-50 p-4 space-y-3"
            role="dialog"
            aria-labelledby="et-sync-popover-title"
          >
            <h2 id="et-sync-popover-title" class="m-0 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">
              Copia en tu cuenta
            </h2>
            <details
              class="group rounded-xl border border-gray-200/90 dark:border-gray-800 bg-gray-50/90 dark:bg-gray-900/45 px-3 py-2.5"
            >
              <summary
                class="cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between gap-2 text-xs font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 select-none"
              >
                <span>Guía rápida</span>
                <span class="text-[10px] font-normal text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 group-open:hidden">Abrir</span>
                <span class="text-[10px] font-normal text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 hidden group-open:inline">Cerrar</span>
              </summary>
              <div class="mt-3 space-y-3 text-xs text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-snug border-t border-gray-200/80 dark:border-gray-800 pt-3">
                <div class="rounded-lg bg-white/80 dark:bg-gray-950/50 border border-gray-200/70 dark:border-gray-700/80 px-2.5 py-2 space-y-1.5">
                  <p class="m-0 font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 text-[11px] uppercase tracking-wide">¿Quién puede ver tus gastos?</p>
                  <ul class="m-0 pl-4 space-y-1 list-disc marker:text-indigo-400">
                    <li><strong class="text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">Solo en el navegador:</strong> no salen de tu equipo.</li>
                    <li><strong class="text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">Copia en cuenta (sin segunda casilla):</strong> la app solo enseña tu copia a tu sesión; otro usuario o un “admin” usando la web con su cuenta <strong class="text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">no entra en tus filas</strong>.</li>
                    <li><strong class="text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">Copia + frase del cuaderno:</strong> en el servidor solo hay caracteres sin sentido; <strong class="text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">sin tu frase no se leen los importes</strong> ni desde la app ni abriendo la base a mano.</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
                <ul class="m-0 pl-4 space-y-2 list-disc marker:text-gray-400">
                  <li>
                    <strong class="text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">Casilla 1 — Guardar en mi cuenta:</strong> misma hoja en varios dispositivos con tu usuario.
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <strong class="text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">Casilla 2 — Proteger con frase:</strong> solo tras la 1. Cifra la copia antes de subirla; hace falta la <strong class="text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">frase del cuaderno</strong> (tú la inventas; no la guardamos).
                  </li>
                </ul>
                <div class="rounded-lg border border-dashed border-gray-300/90 dark:border-gray-600 px-2.5 py-2 space-y-1">
                  <p class="m-0 text-[11px] font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Ejemplo de frase (no la copies tal cual)</p>
                  <p class="m-0 font-mono text-[11px] text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 break-all">gatos-Luna-cafe-2026</p>
                  <p class="m-0 text-[10px] text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-500">Mezcla palabras que recuerdes; mínimo 8 caracteres.</p>
                </div>
                <p class="m-0 text-[11px] text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-500">
                  Orden: 1) cuenta → 2) opcional frase → 3) botón «Elegir o cambiar la frase…». Si olvidas la frase, la copia cifrada no se recupera.
                </p>
              </div>
            </details>
            <p class="m-0 text-[11px] text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Las dos casillas son opcionales.</p>
            <label class="flex items-start gap-3 cursor-pointer">
              <input
                type="checkbox"
                data-et-sync
                class="mt-1 h-4 w-4 rounded border-gray-300 text-indigo-600 focus:ring-indigo-500"
              />
              <span class="text-sm leading-snug">
                <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Guardar también en mi cuenta</span>
                <span class="block text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mt-0.5 text-xs">Misma hoja en otros dispositivos con tu sesión; conexión cifrada.</span>
              </span>
            </label>
            <label class="flex items-start gap-3 cursor-pointer border-t border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-800 pt-3">
              <input
                type="checkbox"
                data-et-cloud-e2e
                class="mt-1 h-4 w-4 rounded border-gray-300 text-indigo-600 focus:ring-indigo-500"
              />
              <span class="text-sm leading-snug">
                <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Proteger la copia con frase</span>
                <span class="block text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mt-0.5 text-xs">Requiere la primera. Sin la frase, la copia en la nube es ilegible. No guardamos la frase.</span>
              </span>
            </label>
            <p class="hidden m-0 text-xs text-amber-800 dark:text-amber-200/95 rounded-lg bg-amber-50/90 dark:bg-amber-950/35 px-2.5 py-2" data-et-e2e-pass-hint>
              Marca «Proteger la copia con frase» y luego pulsa el botón de abajo para escribir la frase del cuaderno (sin ella no se sube nada cifrado).
            </p>
            <button
              type="button"
              data-et-e2e-passphrase
              class="w-full rounded-xl border border-indigo-200 dark:border-indigo-800 bg-indigo-50/80 dark:bg-indigo-950/50 px-3 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-indigo-900 dark:text-indigo-100 hover:bg-indigo-100/80 dark:hover:bg-indigo-900/40"
            >
              Elegir o cambiar la frase del cuaderno…
            </button>
            <div
              class="hidden rounded-xl border border-amber-200/80 dark:border-amber-900/50 bg-amber-50/90 dark:bg-amber-950/30 px-3 py-2.5 text-xs text-amber-950 dark:text-amber-100 space-y-2"
              data-et-e2e-unlock-banner
            >
              <p class="m-0 leading-snug" data-et-e2e-unlock-text></p>
              <button type="button" data-et-e2e-unlock-btn class="w-full rounded-lg bg-amber-200/90 dark:bg-amber-900/50 px-2 py-1.5 font-semibold text-amber-950 dark:text-amber-50">
                Introducir frase y continuar
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="hidden m-0 text-sm text-amber-900 dark:text-amber-100/95 max-w-3xl" data-et-e2e-outside-hint>
        Hay una copia en tu cuenta protegida con frase.
        <button type="button" class="font-semibold underline ml-1" data-et-sync-open-popover>Abrir ajustes</button>
      </p>
    </header>

    <div
      class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200/80 dark:border-gray-800 bg-white/80 dark:bg-gray-950/60 shadow-sm p-4 sm:p-5 space-y-5 dark:[color-scheme:dark]"
      data-et-surface
    >
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-cyan-200/60 dark:border-cyan-900/40 bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-500/10 via-white/80 to-sky-500/5 dark:from-cyan-950/30 dark:via-gray-950/40 dark:to-sky-950/20 px-3 py-2.5 sm:px-4 sm:py-3">
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:flex-wrap sm:items-center gap-2 sm:gap-3">
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-cyan-900/90 dark:text-cyan-200/90 shrink-0">Tipo de cambio</span>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2 min-w-0">
            <span class="text-xs text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 whitespace-nowrap">1 USD →</span>
            <input type="number" step="0.0001" min="0.2" max="5" data-et-fx class="et-field w-24 sm:w-28 font-mono text-sm py-1.5" title="Euros que equivalen a 1 USD" />
            <span class="text-xs text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">EUR</span>
          </div>
          <p class="m-0 text-[11px] text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 font-mono sm:ml-auto min-w-0" data-et-fx-hint></p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col xl:flex-row xl:items-end xl:justify-between gap-4">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-end gap-3 min-w-0">
          <label class="space-y-1">
            <span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Período gastos</span>
            <select data-et-period class="et-field min-w-[10rem] font-medium">
              <option value="30d">Últimos 30 días</option>
              <option value="90d">Últimos 90 días</option>
              <option value="6m">Últimos 6 meses</option>
              <option value="12m">Últimos 12 meses</option>
              <option value="ytd">Este año (YTD)</option>
              <option value="all">Todo</option>
            </select>
          </label>
          <label class="space-y-1">
            <span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Gráficos / totales</span>
            <select data-et-chart-mode class="et-field min-w-[11rem] font-medium">
              <option value="mixed">Mixto (EUR y USD)</option>
              <option value="unify_eur">Unificar en euros</option>
              <option value="unify_usd">Unificar en dólares</option>
            </select>
          </label>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 shrink-0">
          <button type="button" data-et-add-category class="et-btn-secondary">Nueva categoría</button>
          <button type="button" data-et-add-expense class="et-btn-secondary text-sm">Añadir gasto</button>
          <button type="button" data-et-open-sub-modal class="et-btn-accent">Nueva suscripción</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <details class="group rounded-2xl border border-gray-200/90 dark:border-gray-800 bg-gray-50/70 dark:bg-gray-900/35 open:shadow-md">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer list-none px-4 py-3 flex items-center justify-between gap-2 font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">
          <span>Copia de seguridad y archivos</span>
          <span class="text-xs font-normal text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 group-open:hidden">Mostrar ayuda y botones</span>
          <span class="text-xs font-normal text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 hidden group-open:inline">Ocultar</span>
        </summary>
        <div class="px-4 pb-4 pt-0 space-y-4 border-t border-gray-200/80 dark:border-gray-800">
          <p class="m-0 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 max-w-3xl">
            Aquí sacas o metes una copia de <strong class="text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">toda la hoja</strong> (gastos, suscripciones, categorías, recordatorios…).
            <span class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-500">CSV</span> abre en Excel;
            <span class="text-gray-500">JSON</span> es el formato interno exacto (ideal para respaldo);
            <span class="text-gray-500">XLSX</span> es una hoja de cálculo con varias pestañas (misma información que JSON).
          </p>
          <input type="file" accept=".csv,text/csv" class="hidden" data-et-file-csv />
          <input type="file" accept=".json,.txt,application/json" class="hidden" data-et-file-json />
          <input type="file" accept=".xlsx,application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.spreadsheetml.sheet" class="hidden" data-et-file-xlsx />
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <button type="button" data-et-export-csv class="et-btn-secondary text-sm">Descargar CSV</button>
            <button type="button" data-et-export-json class="et-btn-secondary text-sm">Descargar JSON</button>
            <button type="button" data-et-export-xlsx class="et-btn-secondary text-sm">Descargar XLSX</button>
            <button type="button" data-et-import-csv class="et-btn-dashed text-sm">Importar CSV (añade filas)</button>
            <button type="button" data-et-import-json class="et-btn-dashed text-sm">Importar JSON</button>
            <button type="button" data-et-import-xlsx class="et-btn-dashed text-sm">Importar XLSX</button>
          </div>
          <ul class="m-0 pl-5 text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 space-y-1">
            <li><strong class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">CSV:</strong> columnas tipo (<code class="text-[11px]">gasto</code>, <code class="text-[11px]">ingreso</code>, <code class="text-[11px]">suscripcion</code>), fechas, importe, moneda, categoría (puedes usar «Padre / Hijo»), etiquetas, enlaces, notas.</li>
            <li><strong class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">JSON:</strong> al importar, Aceptar fusiona por id; Cancelar sustituye el cuaderno (se mantienen opciones de vista y sync).</li>
            <li><strong class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">XLSX:</strong> mismas reglas que JSON; hojas Gastos, Ingresos, Suscripciones, Recordatorios, Cobros, Meta, TagBank.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </details>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-5 gap-3">
        <div
          class="rounded-2xl border border-emerald-400/35 dark:border-emerald-700/40 bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-500/12 via-gray-50/80 to-white dark:from-emerald-950/25 dark:via-gray-950/60 dark:to-gray-900/80 p-4 shadow-sm"
        >
          <p class="m-0 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-emerald-800/90 dark:text-emerald-300/90">Suscripciones activas</p>
          <p class="mt-1 mb-0 text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50" data-et-kpi-subs>—</p>
          <p class="mt-1 mb-0 text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Coste mensual equivalente (según ciclo)</p>
        </div>
        <div
          class="rounded-2xl border border-sky-400/35 dark:border-sky-700/40 bg-gradient-to-br from-sky-500/12 via-gray-50/80 to-white dark:from-sky-950/25 dark:via-gray-950/60 dark:to-gray-900/80 p-4 shadow-sm"
        >
          <p class="m-0 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-sky-800/90 dark:text-sky-300/90">Gastos en período</p>
          <p class="mt-1 mb-0 text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50" data-et-kpi-expenses>—</p>
          <p class="mt-1 mb-0 text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Suma de filas de la tabla</p>
        </div>
        <div
          class="rounded-2xl border border-teal-400/40 dark:border-teal-800/45 bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-500/14 via-gray-50/80 to-white dark:from-teal-950/30 dark:via-gray-950/60 dark:to-gray-900/80 p-4 shadow-sm"
        >
          <p class="m-0 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-teal-800/90 dark:text-teal-300/90">Ingresos (mes actual)</p>
          <p class="mt-1 mb-0 text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50" data-et-kpi-income>—</p>
          <p class="mt-1 mb-0 text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Cobros previstos + extras en el mes</p>
        </div>
        <div
          class="rounded-2xl border border-rose-400/40 dark:border-rose-900/45 bg-gradient-to-br from-rose-500/12 via-gray-50/80 to-white dark:from-rose-950/25 dark:via-gray-950/60 dark:to-gray-900/80 p-4 shadow-sm"
        >
          <p class="m-0 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-rose-800/90 dark:text-rose-300/90">Balance (mes actual)</p>
          <p class="mt-1 mb-0 text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50" data-et-kpi-balance>—</p>
          <p class="mt-1 mb-0 text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Ingresos − gastos del mes en curso</p>
        </div>
        <div
          class="rounded-2xl border border-violet-400/35 dark:border-violet-700/40 bg-gradient-to-br from-violet-500/12 via-gray-50/80 to-white dark:from-violet-950/25 dark:via-gray-950/60 dark:to-gray-900/80 p-4 shadow-sm sm:col-span-2 xl:col-span-1"
        >
          <p class="m-0 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-violet-800/90 dark:text-violet-300/90">Total combinado (referencia)</p>
          <p class="mt-1 mb-0 text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50" data-et-kpi-blend>—</p>
          <p class="mt-1 mb-0 text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Subs mensual + gastos del período</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-3">
      <h2 class="m-0 text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight">Suscripciones</h2>
      <p class="m-0 text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Toca una tarjeta para editar</p>
      <div
        class="flex gap-3 overflow-x-auto pb-2 -mx-1 px-1 snap-x snap-mandatory scroll-smooth"
        data-et-subs-strip
      >
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="rounded-2xl border border-amber-200/70 dark:border-amber-900/50 bg-amber-50/60 dark:bg-amber-950/20 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-amber-950 dark:text-amber-100 hidden" data-et-remind-banner></div>

    <div class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200/80 dark:border-gray-800 bg-white/80 dark:bg-gray-950/60 shadow-sm" id="et-expenses-table" data-et-expenses-anchor>
      <div class="border-b border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-800 px-4 py-3 flex flex-col gap-3">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-3">
          <h2 class="m-0 text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight">Gastos</h2>
          <button
            type="button"
            data-et-add-expense
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-xl px-4 py-2.5 text-sm font-bold text-white shadow-lg shadow-indigo-500/25 bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-600 via-violet-600 to-fuchsia-600 hover:from-indigo-500 hover:via-violet-500 hover:to-fuchsia-500 focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-indigo-400 focus-visible:ring-offset-2 dark:focus-visible:ring-offset-gray-950 transition"
          >
            <span class="text-lg leading-none font-light">+</span>
            Nuevo gasto
          </button>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-end gap-3">
          <label class="space-y-1">
            <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Mes</span>
            <input type="month" data-et-exp-filter-month class="et-field py-1.5 text-sm w-[11rem] font-mono" />
          </label>
          <label class="space-y-1">
            <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Día</span>
            <select data-et-exp-filter-day class="et-field py-1.5 text-sm w-[8.5rem]">
              <option value="">Todo el mes</option>
              {filterDays.map((d) => (
                <option value={String(d)}>{d}</option>
              ))}
            </select>
          </label>
          <span class="text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 max-w-xl pb-1"
            >Solo se listan filas del mes (y día si lo eliges). Borradores: borde cian; confirmados: tono rojizo.</span
          >
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        class="max-h-[min(55vh,28rem)] overflow-y-auto overflow-x-auto et-expenses-x-scroll rounded-b-2xl"
        data-et-expenses-scroll
      >
        <table class="w-full min-w-[80rem] text-sm border-collapse">
          <thead class="sticky top-0 z-10 bg-gray-50/95 dark:bg-gray-900/90 backdrop-blur-sm">
            <tr class="text-left text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
              <th class="px-3 py-2.5 w-28">Fecha</th>
              <th class="px-3 py-2.5 min-w-[10rem]">Concepto</th>
              <th class="px-3 py-2.5 w-28">Importe</th>
              <th class="px-3 py-2.5 w-24">Moneda</th>
              <th class="px-3 py-2.5 min-w-[9rem]">Categoría</th>
              <th class="px-3 py-2.5 min-w-[9rem]">Etiquetas</th>
              <th class="px-3 py-2.5 min-w-[11rem]">Enlaces</th>
              <th class="px-3 py-2.5 min-w-[8rem]">Notas</th>
              <th class="px-3 py-2.5 w-[7.5rem]">Estado</th>
              <th class="px-3 py-2.5 w-24"></th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody data-et-expenses-body class="divide-y divide-gray-100 dark:divide-gray-800"></tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>

